reviewText:
This movie from MMWW is better than one would guess,How much was filmed in Georgia and how much in Hollyweird is a guess though.

 There is Hollyweird BTS looks with stunts and car crashes,Romances with people wearing little and Alcohol & drugs aplenty.

The cast is really good and fun to watch,Some more than others,The blonde lead female is quit fetching

feCHiNG/

  adjective
  adjective: fetching
  attractive.
  a fetching little garment of pink satin
  synonyms:  attractive, appealing, sweet, pretty, good-looking, lovely, delightful, charming, prepossessing, captivating, enchanting, irresistible;

  bonny;
  informaldivine, heavenly;
  killer;
  archaiccomely, fair
  give this note to the fetching young lady in the blue dress
There are multiple plot lines going on in this movie, which makes it a complex (yet easy to follow) & interesting piece. I was thrilled by the whole thing.
Great concept here and well executed. I enjoyed it from top to bottom. Told several of my friends about this cool movie.

This is a solid indie flick with good writing and acting. I don't want to give too much away about the plot but I will say this movie is a cut above a lot of the shlock I see on cable. Give it a shot.
